lead_paragraph: West Indies players will share the entire $1.6 million in prize money for winning the men's World Twenty20 title as well as a portion of sponsorship revenue, the head of the region's cricket board told Reuters on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Winning Windies Players Will Share Prize Money-CEO
